annotationA: CAAX prenyl protease 2; Proteolytically removes the C-terminal three residues of farnesylated and geranylated proteins
annotationB: Ste24c prenyl protease type I (Ste24c), along with ste24a and ste24b, are paralogous (tandemly duplicated) type I prenyl proteases. Ste24c plays an essential role in the male germline
